&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;应对气候变化的关键是从燃烧化石燃料转向使用可再生能源。但法国历史学家让-巴蒂斯特·弗雷索（Jean-Baptiste Fressoz）在他的著作《&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;越来越多》&lt;/em&gt;中指出，世界以前从未真正成功实现过能源转型，目前的计划也不切实际。许多人认为他的文章意味着阻止全球变暖是不可能的，然而，他本周在《零》节目中告诉 Akshat Rathi，他的观点实际上完全不同。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/3pYttyLLPKMq49oygEk3ndzs_0kjlFxng0dv33zpHfMRuq_jc8Gb7qn05O3Hq9loQ_5VBz1Tqbz_anOXmFXKQmjRwPkki07fIz9Om4Zof6xjPZwYIvDZH7NZfFgUAOIiTmD6AtY2VvdQzOGUw3uQjd6uXIhEJ-a1p6Kecx6oIApd4GnlwJw88Y8lIgLnQuDFRfitwMrgcH5Tv5HIV3KqYsKoXz-4ex9OIPTMBXBY44L0BR39LtgcbiY3BAB9D48VXSM_mKWsazIvohIzmDaE82-lq3jXH12lmg9OuEFHdNiw8SpEQ6AIEEj5uGxfjxpluoW8QigisQ-3ng3U4eMG0j2dSl4/i2A4cc6XKiIE8209_nCdiA0g4MYMjL4c/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="我们需要进行的能源转型辩论 - 零"&gt;立即收听&lt;/a&gt;，并在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/3_CZEz_PTYVCaZ-jI2KJqF83lLPNksqJcwKPGTOP2Fymol4GisHFkcaKQiC3vXL9h35EgRMCIQlUz0b9XAHuycMdUT5t78fCQzpr4d4P_qrTtId4wjgL42upuA8Dgjkp_DxIO8_lTez_IknjmrmfOiNQUJPhn2hEakDVUQLWL_6lU1Xq8-eHEUvSEcFzI5Pu2Cx7phTNcL8CWP82beraJ12Clb99dqh0nICJx2JlQsIeuk5a44FYSIC-tQPP-1qYWjwimEZYbXi6JUlCa70xh7kYFuzgXKYA3Zcf5dHIzGkEYfoH3bKLQ8GLWemG7QpsfSaNZQ/40yx1omOYM8ibeu38JmEdQf-WqHakbPN/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;Apple&lt;/a&gt; 、 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/SqrhRK_4sREvuSn9KB3X7cTZP_ZPZCAogkDNypUvcBvv5lk4KgHoSx8tji9U_kGH8EtvQfCXqi7uZXZh4Qd_X1K7vRXbLwqFjTeIcIx3krWMbHyOmLEP5NjMhJXj_C182oZOYHZAb473HWVO83d5mT082nyKRsmVcV-tA389EjPv31T3PljiJpiDEgNSudCcbYQO2paeJEEc6-3F9mjzlM2MpsdY1Bl6VwWOGy2aKfAumo0lgAUl3NTGq9he7Nwivg6XmGWMs2C2whfUim8b6ES2EWlqwIXQn3qqF9C2eZs5MhjJEygJBMM70u2sFQL8SyqRO4tHI0SE19PvKfPhw4RZ8Avi/XRHf_fR5WA--O2SzkyCEOLpWl7mQ5Qu5/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;Spotify&lt;